source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SEQ_00<tab>Estrild of the Shiokaze Hostelry continues to keep a close, enlisting eye on passersby.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SEQ_00<tab>Une fois encore, Estrild vous sonde du regard.

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_001<tab>Gods be good! It is not every day I see one as strong as you pass by. I am Estrild, of Clan Centurio, and I invite you to take part on our Hunt!

TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_002<tab>Ahhh, but I know your face. Aye, aye, you are the firebrand. The one whose ways have kept <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((him)) /var> from rising through our ranks. <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, was it not?
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_002<tab>Ah, ça y est, ça me revient<var 1D /var>! <var 08 E905 ((La fautrice)) ((Le fauteur)) /var> de troubles <var 08 E905 ((bloquée)) ((bloqué)) /var> aux rangs inférieurs... <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, c'est ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_003<tab>It has been some while since last we met. Your eyes have changed, and that for the better. I'd venture you've had your share of grazes with death since then.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_003<tab>Hé, c'est moi ou tu t'es <var 08 E905 ((aguerrie)) ((aguerri)) /var> depuis la dernière fois<var 1D /var>? Ce regard, c'est celui de quelqu'un qui a contemplé la mort de très près...

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_004<tab>Aye, the one-star bills are no longer fit for you. Go and speak with Wlveva. See if the Clan will not issue you bills more suited to one of your abilities. For as the hunter grows, so too must the hunt!
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_004<tab>Tu dois commencer à t'ennuyer avec les contrats de vétéran de rang un... Si j'étais toi, j'irais voir Wlveva pour qu'elle te donne accès au rang supérieur. Buter des bestioles toujours plus balèzes, y a que ça de vrai<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_010<tab>You must be <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. Estrild told me to expect you. She mentioned it was time you tried your hand at a second star.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_010<tab>Estrild m'a tout dit... Tu veux te frotter à la série de contrats suivante, c'est ça<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_011<tab>It would seem she's taken quite a liking to you. And rightly so. Estrild has always fawned on strong <var 08 E905 ((women)) ((men)) /var>. I suppose there's no faulting her for that.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_011<tab>De moi à toi, je crois que tu lui as tapé dans l'œil. Il ne faut pas lui en vouloir, elle fond dès qu'elle voit <var 08 E905 ((une chasseuse)) ((un chasseur)) /var> un peu <var 08 E905 ((douée)) ((doué)) /var>...

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_012<tab>So be it. I will see to it our two-stars are at your disposal. But you would do well to know the difficulty will be far greater than one-star hunts you've seen. Prepare yourself.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_WLVEVA_000_012<tab>Entendu, à compter de maintenant, tu auras accès aux contrats de vétéran de rang deux. Comme tu peux t'en douter, ils sont bien plus dangereux que ceux de rang un. Tiens-le-toi pour dit.

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_100_013<tab>Two-star Veteran Clan mark bills are now available.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_100_013<tab>Les contrats de vétéran (rang 2) sont désormais disponibles<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>You are now able to undertake two-star Veteran Clan mark bills from the Clan Hunt boards in Kugane and Rhalgr's Reach.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Vous pouvez désormais remplir les contrats de vétéran (rang 2) proposés sur les tableaux des contrats du clan de Kugane et de L'Étendue de Rhalgr.

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>New quests and three-star Veteran Clan mark bills will become available from Estrild at the Shiokaze Hostelry upon reaching level 66.
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>Lorsque vous aurez atteint le niveau 66, Estrild proposera une nouvelle quête donnant accès aux contrats de vétéran (rang 3).

source: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_015<tab>See if the Clan will not issue you bills more suited to one of your abilities. For as the hunter grows, so too must the hunt!
target: TEXT_STMBDY106_02937_ESTRILD_000_015<tab>Si j'étais toi, j'irais voir Wlveva pour qu'elle te donne accès au rang supérieur. Buter des bestioles toujours plus balèzes, y a que ça de vrai<var 1D /var>!
